Text: Dope Wars for Windows Order No Cc Thank you for registering Dope Wars for Windows You can convert the evaluation version to a registered version with the following Registration Key Registration Key IMMIJMMJIIIMMMJ Heres how to enter your Registration Key Start the game and from the main window click on the Registration menu item Click the sub menu item Enter Registration Key A dialog box will appear for you to enter your Registration Key Cut and paste your Registration Key from above into this box and click the Ok button Please save this message for future reference Thanks for your support Comments questions etc are always welcome Beermat Software wwwbeermatsoftwarecom
